                      Incipit: <foreign xml:lang="gez">ስረብዙ፡ ክትክታ፡ ጠንበላል፡ (ጥድ፡ ዝግባ፡ አጠፋሪስ፡ እሬሳ፡ ክምር፡ አረግ፡ እሬሳ፡ ገብስ፡ ቡቃያ፤ ሁልገብ፡ ጐርጠብ፡ ወይናግፍት፡ ወይራ፡ ምሰርች፡ ቀረጥ፡ የምድር፡ እቧይ፡ ቀጠጥና፡ አዘ፡ አረግ፡ ይኸንን፡ ቅጠሉን፡ አንድነት፡ ወቅጦ፡ በሌት፡ ውሀ፡<gap reason="omitted"/></foreign>
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a2">
                    <locus target="#iiiv(erso)" facs="004">Fol. iiiv(erso)</locus>
                    <desc>
                    A Gǝ`ǝz poem called, <foreign xml:lang="gez">መወድስ</foreign>, composed by Mämhǝr Gäbrä Maryam
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e1">
                    <locus target="#ir(ecto) #25v #48r #49v" facs="001 029 051 053">Fols. ir(ecto), 25v, 48r, 49v</locus>
                    <desc>
                    seal of Dr. Tito Lepisa
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a3">
                    <locus target="#iir(ecto)" facs="002">Fol. iir(ecto)</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Table of Contents
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e2">
                    <locus target="#iiv(erso)" facs="003">Fol. iiv(erso)</locus>
                    <desc>
                    Pen trial, mostly erased
                    </desc>
                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="a4">
                    <locus target="#iiir(ecto)" facs="003"> f. iiir(ecto), bottom</locus>
                    <desc>
