                    </item>
                    <item xml:id="e5">
                    <locus target="#2v" facs="006"> f. 2v, line 1</locus><locus target="#21v" facs="025"> f. 21v, line 1</locus><locus target="#38v" facs="042"> f. 38v, line 2</locus><locus target="#40r" facs="043"> f. 40r, line 2</locus><locus target="#43r" facs="046"> f. 43r, line 1</locus><locus target="#6v" facs="010"> f. 6v, line 9</locus>
                    <desc>
                    words of text are written in the upper margin with a symbol (┴) marking the location where the text is to be inserted (2v; 21v; 38v; 40r; 43r), and in another case where the symbol (┬) is used (6v);
